{
  "stem": "4247.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beyond that, in those days-- although I must say, perhaps what I was going to say is not quite correct, because my motherly grandfather was a baker in a small provincial town in-- in Hungary who had eight children, managed to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] achieve professional status for his sons.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was one doctor and two lawyers amongst them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very strangely, one of the girls was a lawyer, which was an unbelievably avant garde activity at those time, particularly for a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One son stayed a baker, and he was the black sheep of the family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the other girls, including my mother, they got married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was their-- their-- their-- their fate, and their destiny-- their destination.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll give you a good example what the expectation was in my grandfather's time, very typical story.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said, there was eight children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The children could not get the type of attention what a child gets in a single child family, like I did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they had eight children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the boys-- whose name was Emery also, I was named after him, who became a doctor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At the age of 14, he was a strong-willed young child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He decided that he had enough of this education.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wants to finish, right?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my grandmother, who was the-- who was wearing the trousers, I believe, in the family, said to him, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] fine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Emery uses a very old legend in the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, they lived in the-- they lived in the Slovak part of Hungary, in the upper part.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came back and he said in Slovak, which is-- I don't understand Slovak, but the word stuck with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SLOVAK].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means, I believe, that I have learned enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
